  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a [寿士(Sushi)], a craftsman who loves sushi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim to become the top sushi king with unique characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online battle for up to 3 people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player who collects two pieces of sushi before the other players wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the side menu to your advantage! ! !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・25 types of popular sushi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can eat sushi (in the game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Grill sushi, order miso soup, and order dessert! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- You can play against random players or against your friends.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a [寿士(Sushi)], a craftsman who loves sushi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim to become the top sushi king with unique characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online battle for up to 3 people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player who collects two pieces of sushi before the other players wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the side menu to your advantage! ! !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・25 types of popular sushi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can eat sushi (in the game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Grill sushi, order miso soup, and order dessert! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- You can play against random players or against your friends.</p>",
